The World's Billionaires#785 Joseph Steinberg03.05.08,
			 6:00 PM ET



  


			<  Previous: Fayez Sarofim  Next: Kerry Stokes >
		

 Age: 64   Fortune: self made   Source: Leucadia National Corp   Net Worth:  $1.5 bil    Country Of Citizenship:  United States   Residence:  New York,  New York
, United States,  North America   Industry:  Investments   Marital Status: married, 3 children   Education: New York University, Bachelor of Arts / Science 
Harvard University, Master of Business Administration
 
Press-shy value investor met partner Ian Cumming at Harvard Business School. Duo bought stake in bankrupt holding company early 1970s; renamed Leucadia National, took full control 1979. Seeks hidden value in companies with depressed stock prices. Firm acquired vacation property manager ResortsQuest International last June for $15 million. Chairman of real estate developer HomeFed. On boards of Premier Entertainment Biloxi (movies), Fortescue (Australian mining).   


