Insider Activity


Individual




Joseph S. Steinberg



Mr. Joseph S. Steinberg is Non-Executive Chairman at Fidelity & Guaranty Life, Chairman at HRG Group, Inc., Independent Director at Crimson Wine Group Ltd., Independent Director at Jefferies Group LLC, Chairman at HomeFed Corp., Chairman at Leucadia National Corp., Chairman at Olympus Re Insurance Co. Ltd., and President at Finova Capital Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc., Crimson Wine Group Ltd., Jefferies Group LLC, Jefferies High Yield Holdings LLC, and New York City Center, Inc.
Mr. Steinberg was previously employed as Independent Director by Mueller Industries, Inc., Non-Executive Director by Fortescue Metals Group Ltd., President & Director by FINOVA Group, Inc., and President by Leucadia National Corp. He also served on the board at Jefferies Investment Advisers LLC, White Mountains Insurance Group Ltd., Jordan Industries, Inc., and Premier Entertainment Biloxi LLC.
He received his undergraduate degree from New York University and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



